RG America, Inc. (RGMI)
docs.description: RG America, Inc. (RG) provides an array of fee-based services that address clients' risk management needs for their real estate assets. This is accomplished by addressing procedures and costs associated with the risk of a possible loss, such as loss control activities and purchasing traditional insurance products. The Company focuses on two main lines of business: Insurance Restoration Services and Financial Services. The Insurance Restoration Services segment comprises the recovery, remediation, reconstruction and roofing divisions. The Financial Services segment includes the insurance and risk management divisions. RG operates in the Insurance Restoration Services Division through its subsidiaries, RG Risk Management, Inc., RG Restoration, Inc., doing business as The Restoration Group, and RG Roofing, Inc. RG operates in the Financial Services Division through its subsidiaries, RG Insurance Services, Inc and RG Financial Services.
